README
------
This is the beta1 release of the HDF5 format checker. This one is for the
HDF5 File Format Specification Version 1.1.

src/  holds h5check library code.
tool/ holds the source code of the h5check tool.
test/ holds the test suite of the h5check tool.
doc/  holds all document related to the tool

========
To build:
========
Assuming gcc, gmake and h5cc are in your $PATH, just do
    % ./configure
    % gmake
    
If you want to use a different C compiler and/or h5cc command, do
    % make CC=gcc H5CC=mypath/h5cc
    
============
To run tests:
============
    % gmake check

==========
To install:
==========
To install,
    % gmake install
These go to /usr/local/{bin,lib} by default.  If you want to install it
somewhere else like /usr/software/{bin,lib},
    % gmake prefix=/usr/software install

===================
Platforms supported:
===================
Linux 2.6 (32bit), Solaris 10
Being ported: AIX 5.3, Linux 2.6 (64bit)

========
Question:
========
Email help@hdfgroup.org.

